{"tid":1505741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強 烈 要 求 viutv 開 番 個 24 小 時 新 聞 台","createTime":"2019-08-25T15:27:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T04:55:22.000Z","uid":2599,"like":155,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"7d26edd4cfbdac30e86eb530e4f41365d1b3a213","tid":1505741,"uid":2599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:27:07.000Z","msg":"其實睇得出viutv好努力搞唔同節目想谷起收視<br />\n但無奈香港人慣性收視只睇cctvb<br />\n強烈建議viutv開番個24小時新聞台嚟制衡cctvb83台<br />\nViutv本身又有now免費新聞台 唔會有額外成本<br />\n又可以廣告之間加插自己啲節目預告增加收視<br />\n又可以令更多中老年人唔會淨係俾cctvb啲新聞荼毒<br />\n雖然rthk 31 32台都有新聞直播<br />\n但有好多老年人都較鍾意傳統搵新聞廣播員報道<br />\n至少我家兩老係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果viutv真係搞番個新聞台<br />\n我相信有好多手足出街食飯都會幫手轉台<br />\n<br />\n最後想講啲係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無線新聞 出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c92c9887222f70502f032d386feb86cbe62d1c30","tid":1505741,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T15:27:21.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 文宣集合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1505474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1505474</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#推到有英文文宣#</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#黑警還眼 #612 #721 #811 #823</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rt9LBCx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frt9LBCx.jpg&h=73c530e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3kZESP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna